org.modelio.api.modelio.editor

Interface IMDAEditorListener


  • public interface IMDAEditorListener
    After opening a IMDATextEditor, a listener can be added to it using the setListener(IMDAEditorListener listener) method.

    When the specified event occurs, documentSaved(...) or editorClosed(...) will be sent to the instance.

    See Also:
